replies.body:
Good idea, but maybe instead of procing with his W maybe it could be a part of his passive, where every time he kills he gets a mobility boost. That might be better, as you can pop your w a lot more times than killing an enemy opponent to get the mobility boost. As for minion kills for the boost, it can be reduced like the AS buff in the passive. It might be cool to gain mobility when u hit your E against an enemy (initial hit only) or with any ability too, but that might be pushing it

But Varus FTW 
